Opensocial
==========

Provides a helper method in the routing to set a number of named routes, to
access controllers as if they were OpenSocial resources. 

Adds an OpenSocial mime-type.


Example
=======

map.opensocial_people :users do |user|
  user.opensocial_friends :friends
  user.opensocial_activities :activities
end


